    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Subway Outbreak is a side-scrolling base defense strategy pixel game. <br>In this short demo you play the role of the survivor in the metro station.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266260/extras/f8815a595f629ee3c03d0add8ed3c627.poster.avif?t=1748026768\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266260/extras/f8815a595f629ee3c03d0add8ed3c627.webm?t=1748026768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266260/extras/f8815a595f629ee3c03d0add8ed3c627.mp4?t=1748026768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What to do in the Demo</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your goal will be to survive 5 days by collecting food and scrap to build out your base to defend against the horde of mutants. Be sure to collect more civilians to defend your base and explore the tunnels.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266260/extras/e1d27d101314b95a18300d4a88426bfd.poster.avif?t=1748026768\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266260/extras/e1d27d101314b95a18300d4a88426bfd.webm?t=1748026768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266260/extras/e1d27d101314b95a18300d4a88426bfd.mp4?t=1748026768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Are you ready?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be sure your ready for day 5 or this will be the end of your game.</p>",
